Path: godot/tutorials/animation/cutout_animation.rst
Summary: Explains how skeletal deformation can be used to enhance cutout rigs for organic movement.
Skeletal deform can be used to augment a cutout rig, allowing single pieces to deform organically (e.g. antennae that wobble as an insect character walks). This process is described in a separate tutorial.